On International Day for the Elimination of Violence Against Women we honor: 

🟡 The thousands of Palestinian women Israel has killed in Gaza; 

🟡 the thousands of Palestinian women whose children Israel has killed in Gaza; 

🟡 the tens of thousands more Palestinian women whose homes Israel has destroyed and stolen in Gaza and across occupied Palestine; 

🟡 the thousands of Palestinian women unjustly detained in Israeli jails where they are subjected to sexual abuse and torture; 

🟡 the millions of Palestinian women who risk their lives to resist Israeli genocide, occupation and apartheid.

